data.description: NOW OFFERING: SELLER WILL BUY 2 POINTS TO REDUCE YOUR INTEREST RATE! Max value of $10,000. This home offers year round mtn views, over 4 acres, 15 mins to downtown Asheville. Enjoy the front porch mtn views and soak up the Blue Ridge Mtns. The main level offers a spacious living room, kitchen. and a large primary bedroom. An office on the main level makes working from home easy. Upstairs you will find two large bedrooms with a full bathroom in between. On the lower level is a finished space that makes for a great media/game/excercise room. A true two car garage prevents the need for carrying the groceries in the rain. The wrap around partially covered deck expands the entertainment area rain or shine. The gravel road leading to the home is not steep and does not require a 4x4. All of this just 10 mins from Blk Mtn and 15 mins to Asheville. Neighborhood DOES allow short term rentals.
